snippet.title: Ember Knights - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for Ember Knights: a fast-paced dungeon-crawling multiplayer rogue-lite by Tiny Titan Studios!
Try the already available demo and make sure to wishlist the game: https://bit.ly/2SK6oka
Join the community on: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/emberknightsgame 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheEmberKnights 
Discord: https://t.co/o08c3xSX8h?amp=1
